north - Move to the room in the north direction
south - Move to the room in the south direction
east - Move to the room in the east direction
west - Move to the room in the west direction
go - Move directly to a room have been in before
look - Get information about an object or place
inventory - List all the items in your inventory
use - Use an item in your inventory on an object in the room you are in
get - Pick up an item from the room you are in and put it in your inventory
drop - Place an item from your inventory into the room you are in
help - Produces the list you are currently looking at
exit - Quit the game (NOTE: there is no save feature)